,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T14:56:48.000Z","msg":"明白樓豬個老母點解唔幫樓豬移民<br />\n樓豬打得支那工，就要預一生一世係大灣區<br />\n阿門"},{"pid":"98723a2823319e2a4de21303761323b3caa359a0","tid":2046704,"uid":228934,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T15:01:25.000Z","msg":"黃屍老母曰<br />\n公務員邊有黃絲，工作已經將你定性。實際上上司講乜就盲執行，到自己管理下屬都係靠威迫利誘，無靈魂，除左最叻講是非外，辨別黑白是非就....... 一尾刷鞋搏上司寫靚Report 搏升，仲有乜資格話自己係黃絲。<br />\n<br />\n服務市民只係你留低既藉口，睇怕年中做過唔知幾多白痴野難為左幾多無知市民。老細吹雞，全部跪低。工會班老鬼要刷鞋凍薪三年，睇怕你地都準備要盲跟，應該整張自願凍薪form比你班友簽，睇下到時幾多人敢唔簽。"},{"pid":"ca4f7590f8edf1342f58e1f271af052c35520f50","tid":2046704,"uid":228934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"69fd12f3b28e61acfdb580aa9a7c05869b7f8537","tid":2046704,"uid":276273,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T14:56:48.000Z","msg":"明白樓豬個老母點解唔幫樓豬移民<br />\n樓豬打得支那工，就要預一生一世係大灣區<br />\n阿門"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T15:02:02.000Z","msg":"係呀 樓豬朋友同樓豬老母已經斷絕關係"},{"pid":"923e62328e5c44374f3df18d18be75519cc368ee","tid":2046704,"uid":228934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5c6340fbb4e7df9e1f8335d89071faded27d723","tid":2046704,"uid":195169,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"06ab67c3d64ef04691f5600cdcac71e41944b81f","tid":2046704,"uid":228934,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"35507a81f877efd18d262c50645e20833c608ff5","tid":2046704,"uid":195169,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T14:50:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />羡慕樓主有個好老母<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T14:53:29.000Z","msg":"居然<br />\n<br />\n擺撚明病態鬥黃"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T14:55:42.000Z","msg":"屌你我成家藍蛆啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T15:02:39.000Z","msg"